-- APPENDIX P : MIGRATION NOTES (v2.0 -> v2.5)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- No public API changes.  Existing scripts using Theme = 'Amethyst',
-- 'Sunset', 'Midnight', 'Forest', 'Cyber', 'Aurora' or 'Mono' still load,
-- but the theme is silently aliased to one of the 3 core palettes.
-- If you want an exact colour, switch Theme to 'Ocean', 'MatrixGreen' or
-- 'Crimson' directly.
-- 
-- The animated FX layers respect Aquafield._hidden, so calling :Hide()
-- also pauses the Heartbeat updates for free.
-- 
-- Closing the window now calls saveConfig() before destroying the ScreenGui
-- to preserve toggle / slider / dropdown / colour state when
-- ConfigurationSaving is enabled (this was already the v2.0 behaviour, but
-- with the new lucide ImageButton click target the hit-box is reliable on
-- touchscreens for the first time).
--
